"title": "5505: roads",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5505: roads",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Recognised routes for travellers, or streets in towns and cities. In biblical times travelling by road was recognised as dangerous.</p>\n<h2>Kinds of road</h2>\n<h3>In the open country</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:17-Exod13:18\">EXO 13:17–13:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:1\">ACT 19:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:7\">GEN 16:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:17\">NUM 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:2\">DEU 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:10-Josh10:11\">JOS 10:10–10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg21:19\">JDG 21:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:52\">1SA 17:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa15:5\">ISA 15:5</a></p>\n<h3>In towns and cities</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:11\">ACT 9:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth6:9\">EST 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:21\">JER 37:21</a></p>\n<h2>Activities associated with roads and streets</h2>\n<h3>Travelling</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:10\">JDG 5:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:23\">2KI 2:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:57\">LUK 9:57</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:30-Luke10:33\">LUK 10:30–10:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:36\">ACT 8:36</a></p>\n<h3>Talking</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:32\">LUK 24:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:7\">DEU 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:33\">MRK 9:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:4\">LUK 10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:26\">LUK 13:26</a></p>\n<h3>Waiting</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:13\">1SA 4:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:2\">2SA 15:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:38\">1KI 20:38</a></p>\n<h3>Helping others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:4\">DEU 22:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:18\">DEU 27:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:30-Luke10:33\">LUK 10:30–10:33</a></p>\n<h3>Leisure and play</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:4-Zech8:5\">ZEC 8:4–8:5</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Begging</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:35\">LUK 18:35</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Living on the streets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:9-Matt22:10\">MAT 22:9–22:10</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:21-Luke14:23\">LUK 14:21–14:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:32\">JOB 31:32</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:5\">MAT 6:5</a></p>\n<h3>Idolatry</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:24\">2CH 28:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:17\">JER 44:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:25\">EZK 16:25</a></p>\n<h3>Injustice and dishonesty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:14\">ISA 59:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:1\">JER 5:1</a></p>\n<h2>Dangers of the road</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:31\">EZR 8:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs13:24\">1KI 13:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:22\">EZR 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:5\">ECC 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:13\">PRO 22:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:1\">HOS 7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:30-Luke10:33\">LUK 10:30–10:33</a></p>\n<h2>Troubled times affecting roads and streets</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:11\">PSA 55:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah2:4\">NAM 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:19\">JOS 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:25\">JER 6:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:9\">HOS 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:25\">ISA 5:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:7-Isa33:8\">ISA 33:7–33:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:20\">ISA 51:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:16\">AMO 5:16</a></p>\n<h3>Roads and streets deserted</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:6\">JDG 5:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:21\">JER 9:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:10\">JER 33:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:4\">LAM 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:6\">ZEP 3:6</a></p>\n<h3>Escape</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:19\">JER 48:19</a></p>\n<h2>The road back from exile</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:3\">ISA 40:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:16\">ISA 11:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:8\">ISA 35:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:14\">ISA 57:14</a></p>\n<h2>Roads used figuratively</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:13-Matt7:14\">MAT 7:13–7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:17\">GEN 49:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:19\">PRO 15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:8\">ISA 59:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:2\">JER 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:15\">JER 18:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:21\">JER 31:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:5\">LUK 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:2\">REV 22:2</a></p>\n<h2>Roads of special importance in the NT</h2>\n<h3>The road to Emmaus</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:13-Luke24:32\">LUK 24:13–24:32</a></p>\n<h3>The road to Damascus</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:3-Acts9:9\">ACT 9:3–9:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:17\">ACT 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:6\">ACT 22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:13\">ACT 26:13</a></p>",
